npm install
    can install all the dependencies of the module from the package.json file

express
    Node.js web app framework that provides broad features for building web and mobile applications
    it can build single/multi/hybrid web app that can manage servers and routes
    express helps us to:
        start a server to listen for requests
        parse incoming requests
        match those requests to particular routes
        craft our http response and associated content

npm init -y
    initialize the node application
    -y flag skips the necessary information

query strings
    comes after the ? in the url
    key value pairs are separated by the ampersand(&)
    
